have waited up for me.

257
00:16:25,151 --> 00:16:27,743
Where in God’s name
have you been?

258
00:16:27,950 --> 00:16:30,536
He’s got a fever.
You’re gonna kill him out there.

259
00:16:32,533 --> 00:16:33,659
Ruthie...

260
00:16:36,454 --> 00:16:38,187
Let me take you back to bed.

261
00:16:39,398 --> 00:16:41,164
Everything’s gonna be fine.

262
00:16:43,361 --> 00:16:45,280
