281
00:18:31,193 --> 00:18:34,161
<i>♪ And I gobble him right down ♪</i>

282
00:18:34,196 --> 00:18:35,830
<i>♪ When they’re inside me‐‐ ♪</i>

283
00:18:35,865 --> 00:18:40,334
SMALL CROWD:
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

284
00:18:40,369 --> 00:18:44,213
♪ Happy birthday
to you ♪

285
00:18:44,248 --> 00:18:48,926
♪ Happy birthday, dear Gordy ♪

286
00:18:48,961 --> 00:18:52,757
♪ Happy birthday to you ♪

287
00:18:56,135 --> 00:18:58,978
‐ ANGELA: Yay! Good job!
‐ DAD: Yay!

288
00:18:59,013 --> 00:19:00,646
Nice job, buddy.

289
00:19:00,681 --> 00:19:02,857
Big brother’s birthday!
Look. Ready?

290
00:19:02,892 --> 00:19:06,402
ANGELA: All right. Now, do you
want an end piece or...

291
00:19:06,437 --> 00:19:08,362
GORDY:
End piece, please.

292
00:19:08,397 --> 00:19:10,117
‐ ANGELA: Ready?
‐ DAD: There you go, buddy.

293
00:19:14,945 --> 00:19:16,505
‐ DAD: Open your presents?
‐ GORDY: Yes!

294
00:19:17,990 --> 00:19:20,207
‐ DAD: I wonder...
‐ ANGELA: Of course you do,

295
00:19:20,242 --> 00:19:21,834
